    "line_items": "Major errors detected: 'Pork' and 'Pancakes' were merged into a single description ('Pork Pancakes'), and the subsequent prices are misaligned with their respective descriptions (e.g., 'Side Bacon' is assigned the price of 'Pancakes'). The item '$3.00 each' was omitted entirely."
